import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import App from './App'

let counter = 1

ReactDOM.render(
  <App counter={counter} />, 
  document.getElementById('root')
)


const refresh = () => {
  ReactDOM.render(<App counter={counter} />, 
  document.getElementById('root'))
}

refresh()
counter += 1
refresh()
counter += 1
refresh()
